---
---

<section id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <p class="section-description">
      Everything you need to build and deploy modern applications
    </p>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Lightning Fast</h3>
        <p>Optimized performance ensures your applications run at peak speed with minimal latency.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Secure by Default</h3>
        <p>Enterprise-grade security built-in from the ground up to protect your data and applications.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
        <h3>Scalable</h3>
        <p>Automatically scale your infrastructure up or down based on demand without manual intervention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🛠️</div>
        <h3>Developer Friendly</h3>
        <p>Intuitive APIs and comprehensive documentation make integration a breeze for developers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
        <h3>Global CDN</h3>
        <p>Deliver content to users worldwide with our distributed network of edge locations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Cost Effective</h3>
        <p>Pay only for what you use with transparent pricing and no hidden fees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
